title: S&P 500 Snaps 3-Week Losing Street Ahead Of Powell's Congressional Report, February Jobs Report Next Week - SPDR S&P 500  ( ARCA:SPY )
description: The SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust SPY snapped a three-week losing streak as investors digested the latest interest rate commentary from Federal Reserve officials.

title: Oracle Reports After The Close On 3/9 -- Options Contracts Expire The Next Day
description: According to NextEarningsDate.com, the Oracle next earnings date is projected to be 3/9 after the close, with earnings estimates of $1.20/share on $12.42 Billion of revenue.

title: Siebel: 'AI is now basically at the top of every CEO's agenda'
description: Tom Siebel has some animated words for all the tech CEOs now pontificating on the virtues of AI.

title: Data Fabric Market Size Expected to Rise USD 6.97 Billion, at a 22.3% CAGR by 2029
description: Pune,India, March 03, 2023 ( GLOBE NEWSWIRE ) -- The global Data Fabric Market Size stood at USD 1.43 billion in 2021. The market is anticipated to rise from USD 1.71 billion in 2022 to USD 6.97 billion by 2029 at a 22.3% CAGR during the forecast period.

title: Oracle  ( NYSE:ORCL )  Downgraded by StockNews.com
description: Oracle ( NYSE:ORCL - Get Rating ) was downgraded by analysts at StockNews.com from a "buy" rating to a "hold" rating in a research note issued on Wednesday. Other equities research analysts have also issued research reports about the stock.

title: Oracle  ( NYSE:ORCL )  Stock Rating Lowered by StockNews.com
description: Oracle ( NYSE:ORCL - Get Rating ) was downgraded by StockNews.com from a "buy" rating to a "hold" rating in a research note issued on Wednesday. A number of other equities research analysts have also recently weighed in on the company.
